---
import ContactForm from '../components/ContactForm.astro';
import { AUTHOR_NAME, AUTHOR_URL, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';

const faqs = [
	{
		q: 'Do you only work with tech companies?',
		a: 'No — the opposite. Main-street businesses are the point: salons, repair shops, law firms, clinics, agencies. If your team runs on phones, calendars, and repetitive admin work, that is exactly where agentic systems earn their keep.',
	},
	{
		q: 'How much does this cost?',
		a: 'Scoping is free. You tell us what you are trying to automate, we tell you what an agent can and cannot do for it, and what a build would involve. You only pay if we agree there is something worth building.',
	},
	{
		q: 'Will you tell me if AI agents are the wrong tool?',
		a: 'Yes, in writing. Plenty of problems are better solved with a checklist, a calendar rule, or a part-time hire. Saying so costs us a project and saves you a bad quarter — that trade is fine with us.',
	},
	{
		q: 'Who actually does the work?',
		a: `${AUTHOR_NAME}, a software engineer who builds verification-gated agent systems — the same approach that runs this site's autonomous editor. No outsourcing, no hand-offs.`,
	},
];

const jsonLd = {
	'@context': 'https://schema.org',
	'@graph': [
		{
			'@type': 'ContactPage',
			name: `Contact ${SITE_TITLE}`,
			url: new URL('/contact/', Astro.site).toString(),
			description:
				'Tell us what you are trying to automate. A real person reads every message and replies within two business days.',
		},
		{
			'@type': 'FAQPage',
			mainEntity: faqs.map(({ q, a }) => ({
				'@type': 'Question',
				name: q,
				acceptedAnswer: { '@type': 'Answer', text: a },
			})),
		},
	],
};
---

<Layout
	title="Work With Us — Contact Vertical Agent Solutions"
	description="Tell us what you're trying to automate. A real person reads every message and replies within two business days — honest advice, even when the answer is 'you don't need an agent.'"
	pubDate={new Date('Jul 12 2026')}
	isArticle={false}
>
	<script is:inline type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(jsonLd)} />
	<p>
		Reading is the start. If your team wants to actually deploy agentic systems — to automate the
		repetitive, augment the skilled, and move faster than competitors still doing it by hand —
		that's what we build. Tell us where you're stuck and we'll tell you whether agents are the
		right tool for it, honestly, including when they're not.
	</p>

	<h2>What happens when you write to us</h2>
	<p>
		The guides on this site are written by an autonomous editor, but this inbox is not. Your
		message lands directly on <a href={AUTHOR_URL}>{AUTHOR_NAME}</a>'s phone. A real person reads
		every message and replies by email, usually within one to two business days (US Eastern
		hours). No automated replies, no sales sequence, and your address never goes on a mailing
		list.
	</p>

	<h2>What to include</h2>
	<ul>
		<li><strong>Your industry</strong> — a salon books differently than a law firm intake desk.</li>
		<li>
			<strong>The repetitive task eating your hours</strong> — missed calls, follow-ups, scheduling,
			data entry, whatever it is.
		</li>
		<li>
			<strong>The tools you already use</strong> — your calendar, booking system, or practice
			software, so we can tell you what an agent could actually plug into.
		</li>
	</ul>

	<h2>Common questions</h2>
	{
		faqs.map(({ q, a }) => (
			<>
				<h3>{q}</h3>
				<p>{a}</p>
			</>
		))
	}

	<h2>Send us a message</h2>
	<ContactForm />
</Layout>
